window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Dungeon Crawler Carl series has exploded in popularity and become a LitRPG sensation since the release of the first installment in 2021. After the release of book 7, <i>This Inevitable Ruin,</i> author Matt Dinniman looks back at the progression of his career with Audible Editor Sam. He reveals how he writes for audio first, takes a lot of joy in sourcing loot-box contents and character names from his fans, and how the whole series was inspired by a little cat named Princess Donut.</p>"; 
